    "body": "This can be implemented by adding a context with timeout here:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/a2b7481b7876439d6e4659b377b96f8c36ec1e03/graphql/service.go#L43-L46\r\n\r\n\r\n```go\r\nctx, cancel = context.WithTimeout(r.Context(), 60 * time.Second)\r\ndefer cancel()\r\n\r\nresponse := h.Schema.Exec(ctx, params.Query, params.OperationName, params.Variables)\r\n```",
